l automatically open your entire snippet library in any app or one that allows you to automatically turn any copied text into a new snippet.\n\n\n\nGet Your iPad Working for You\n\n\n\nThe most recent iPad releases have turned these devices from nice to have tools into serious contenders for replacing your traditional laptop. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBy understanding how to best use your iPad such as using a mechanical keyboard and downloading the most useful apps, you will be able to get your iPad working harder for you.\n\n\n\nDo you use an iPad for work?\n\n\n\nRead more on how to use TextExpander on your iPad.",
